> Gently Air-Dried dog food cooked at low temperatures to preserve the essential nutrients. A healthy, tastier alternative to kibble which is delivered straight to your door and can be conveniently stored in your pantry. Made with 100% real, whole ingredients. No artificial flavors or fillers. Supports improved digestion, healthier skin, shinier coats, immunity and increased energy levels. Made in the USA, with the world's finest ingredients.

> All recipes are developed with vets and are AAFCO complete and balanced for all life stages and all sizes. Feeding & transition instructions included within your delivered box. Roughly 2 weeks of food for a 20Lb adult dog. This box includes 3Lbs of Beef & Berries.

